social_posts.post_text:
The last several weeks have been incredible! Much love to everyone who showed up in Wilmy, last Friday for my bro @louistherapper’s album preview party!!! That was a movie!!!

Other highlights:
• My bestie/graphic designer @ssunshit and I got the @tsc__ent logo tatted on us
• I met one of my favorite comedians, @hannibalburess and got to kick it with him a bit
• I did a pop-up set @ the beach bar 🔥
• Got my first mix back for the new album 🤐

This will probably be my last post of 2022. Huge year ahead of us! I have a lot of new music ready for you to hear. 

Follow @tsc__ent .

Show photos by @asipofbrycetea

My new single, ‘GOIN’ CRAZY’ is now streaming worldwide! I’m very excited to share this with you! The best part is: we’re just getting this journey started….

This song would not have been what it is today, without the genius of super-producer @jesseshirtsmusic and the truly gifted @bahrbeats, who mixed and mastered the track. 🙌🏽 🎸🎚️🎛️

HUGE shoutout to my incredible visual team, @fultonbrand for the fantastic photography and @ssunshit for the stellar graphic artistry. 🥲 📸 🎨 

Lastly, I’d like to thank all of my fans!! The Day-1’s ☝🏾 and my new fans here in the US and all over the world 🌍 🫶🏾

I have so much more new music to share with you 💽 

For now, let’s go crazy together 🤪

July was a GREAT month! Definitely one for the books! Hit Athens, GA and also ended up headlining *TWO* VERY dope shows in my hometown- Brooklyn, NY! HUGE shoutout to my squad @tsc__ent, @secretpour for having us in Brooklyn, @trvyandtheenemy for having us in Athens, and @dyebones @goodfortunesproject @kmg_studio & @jagermeisterusa for having us back in NYC to turn up @ the pop-up!! Most definitely a top-five experience for me!!!!!

MUCH love to all of my Brooklyn friends and family for coming through to these shows and supporting. Glad y’all had a good time! Also got to bring my bro, @louistherapper to my hood for the first time 😂Glad you could make it, bro!

August will be just as busy and I’ll be announcing show dates VERY, VERY soon…

Oh yeah…I also dropped my latest single, “GOIN’ CRAZY” a few weeks ago, so def give that a spin 🤪
